00:07:45,915 --> 00:07:48,228
This is the SFT for Kampala

138
00:07:48,565 --> 00:07:50,490
also prepared by SANDEC.

139
00:07:50,690 --> 00:07:55,090
<i>We see safely managed 
excreta at 48%.</i>

140
00:07:55,793 --> 00:07:59,331
<i>And unsafely managed
