already operating at capacity</i>

143
00:08:07,896 --> 00:08:10,034
<i>within the first month
it was built.</i>

144
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,938
<i>To address this,</i>

145
00:08:12,264 --> 00:08:16,402
<i>NWSC reopened the Bugoloobi
Waste Water Treatment Plant</i>

146
00:08:16,696 --> 00:08:18,896
<i>for discharge of 
faecal sludge</i>

147
00:08:19,096 --> 00:08:22,446
<i>which is not ideal as it's now
over capacitated,</i>

148
00:08:22,646 --> 00:08:26,108
<i>but much better than the 
alternative of illegal dumping.</i>

149
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:30,155
<i>In good news, Bugoloobi
is under renovation</i>

150
00:08:30,598 --> 00:08:34,435
<i>and there are 2 more faecal
sludge treatment plants called for</i>

151
00:08:34,635 --> 00:08:36,848
<i>in the sanitation master plan.</i>

152
00:08:37,048 --> 00:08:39,460
<i>One of which, is in
the planning phase</i>

153
00:08:39,660 --> 00:08:41,885
<i>but not yet in the
