154
00:08:42,917 --> 00:08:45,429
Japan is a country
where on site

155
00:08:45,629 --> 00:08:49,517
and centralised sewer based 
solutions  have evolved in parallel.

156
00:08:50,403 --> 00:08:52,916
Japan can be held up
as an example

157
00:08:53,116 --> 00:08:55,828
of how faecal sludge 
management can work

158
00:08:56,028 --> 00:08:57,778
as a long term solution.

159
00:08:58,654 --> 00:09:02,467
<i>There is an effective system of
collection and transport in place</i>

160
00:09:02,667 --> 00:09:05,842
<i>with discharge to treatment
plants subsidised.</i>

161
00:09:07,153 --> 00:09:10,428
<i>There are well organised and 
functioning treatment plants.</i>

